{"type": "article", "id": 22819, "title": "“香蕉”音响", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-25T07:36:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145826mD25bAPktJLTu9YV.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个便携式音箱，黄色的弧形外观让它像一个香蕉。它的确采用了“剥皮”式的设计，扬声器外面的“皮”可以剥开，通过钕磁铁粘在香蕉另外一侧，既成为一个挂钩，也将扬声器的格栅露出来，在时尚感的外形下带有一份趣味。音响是优质硅胶材质，附有 USB 充电接口、3.5 毫米音频插孔和 LED 灯，也可以通过蓝牙与智能手机连接。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145823FJ6bYwdQRrjVeSDX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.78850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145823MnjH8DFNCytTweBJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87652812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021458243qIgmNWBSKxUoGLJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90464548\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214582565IfhyuVqjE9OYPw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94865526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145825uBYcVJiGILfXgtMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.02933985\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}